An array can be converted to heap

If Heap array is created from tree following then fill array as level order traversal

HEAP is complete binary tree.


priority queue:
By default priority queueu in cpp is max_heap


struct comp {
    bool operator() (ListNode *l, ListNode* r){
        return l->val > r->val;
    }   
};
priority_queue<ListNode*, vector<ListNode*>, comp> pq;        //min heap